snippet.title: THEMIS - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Challenge both your reflexes and the brain cells in the puzzle platformer THEMIS. Your new purpose is clear - successfully finish The Sequence and do as being told by The First One. Sounds simple enough...?

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3134920/THEMIS/
